Cant see the "dev" version of FHIR as http://build.fhir.org/ is returning a 404 at the moment, but ...

Condition.clinicalStatus is of type "Code" with a binding strength of "preferred". If this was profiled to a different set of value where would the codeSystem go?
@Richard Kavanagh Yes, it's a known issue. The spec has grown too large and the migration process to push it to build.fhir.org is timing out. We're working on it.
@Lloyd McKenzie Would it be possible to restore the previous build while you're working out the issue?
I can't. @Josh Mandel @Grahame Grieve ?
it's not a timing out issue. I don't know what the issue is
@Grahame Grieve Are we able to restore the old one to build.fhir.org until we get this figured out?
